'''印度革命马克思主义党'''（{{lang-en|Revolutionary Marxist Party of India}}，缩写为RMPI）是[[印度|印度]]的一个[[共产主义|共产主义]]政党。该党成立于2017年，由[[革命马克思主义党|革命马克思主义党]]和10个左右较小的[[左翼|左翼]]政党合并而成。该党的政治立场是左翼。该党的意识形态是共产主义、[[马克思列宁主义|马克思列宁主义]]。该党的总书记是Mangat Ram Pasla。该党的总部位于[[旁遮普邦|旁遮普邦]][[贾朗达尔|贾朗达尔]]。该党是[[旁遮普民主联盟|旁遮普民主联盟]]的成员<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/thiruvananthapuram/cpm-rmpi-alliance-in-punjab-shocks-state-units/articleshow/56396061.cms|title=CPM-Revolutionary marxist party of Indiaalliance in Punjab shocks state units - Times of India|website=The Times of India|access-date=2019-02-04|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001154230/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/thiruvananthapuram/cpm-rmpi-alliance-in-punjab-shocks-state-units/articleshow/56396061.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dailypost.in/uncategorized/new-political-outfit-revolutionary-marxist-party-india-launched/|title=New political outfit-Revolutionary Marxist Party of India launched|date=2016-09-18|website=Latest Punjab News, Breaking News Punjab, India News {{!}} Daily Post|language=en-US|access-date=2019-02-04|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424002700/https://dailypost.in/uncategorized/new-political-outfit-revolutionary-marxist-party-india-launched/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

